    <p>
    Apart from it's regularly scheduled classes, Jhargram Art Academy also does other forms
    of projects, activities and events adjacent to the world of art, creativity, culture and
    nature. Jhargram Art Academy has been doing annual art exhibitions and festival with the
    paintings and craft works of all it's students while also giving a platform for all rural
    artisans of West Bengal to show their crafts. We have done many puppet theatrical productions
    and dance dramas depicting stories from bengali folklores, to tackling many societal issues,
    to expressing the love for nature.
    </p>
